    Get last millesime

    last_millesime.Rd

    Get last millesime

    last_millesime(data)

    Arguments

    data

    a datafiles tibble (as returned by the datafiles() function)

    Value

    a tibble with the last millesimes for all input datafiles

    Examples

    datafiles() %>% last_millesime()
